App Name: Personality Trait Test
App Package Name: com.aadi.personalityrelaittest

Brief: Personality Trait Test is an enlightening mobile application designed to help individuals uncover the depths of their personality. Grounded in the methodologies of the Briggs Myers theory and inspired by Carl Jung's research, the app offers users the chance to explore their personality type with a comprehensive assessment. With the vision that self-awareness can lead to personal growth, better careers, and enhanced relationships, this app provides an interactive and insightful way to learn about oneself and others.
